trans-unit.source: "No tienes que comer menos, solo tienes que comer mejor."
trans-unit.target: "You don't have to eat less, you just have to eat better."

trans-unit.source: Experimenta nuevos sabores y vive experiencias a través de la comida saludable.
trans-unit.target: Experience new flavors and live experiences through healthy food.

trans-unit.source: Para poder conseguir el cambio que queremos, es importante tener un objetivo y estar motivado. Por eso, en NutriFeed tenemos una comunidad interactiva en que la puedes compartir tu progreso.
trans-unit.target: In order to achieve the change we want, it is important to have a goal and be motivated. That's why at NutriFeed we have an interactive community where you can share your progress.

trans-unit.source: Sube tus fotos, recetas y dietas. Formar parte de la comunidad te ayudará a visualizar tu progreso.
trans-unit.target: Upload your photos, recipes and diets. Being part of the community will help you visualize your progress.

trans-unit.target: Following a diet can be tricky
